#. <section class="sutta" id="sn23.3"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn23.3:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 23"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 23"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn23.3:0.2"
msgid "1. Paṭhamamāravagga"
msgstr "1. About Māra"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn23.3:0.3"
msgid "3. Bhavanettisutta"
msgstr "3. Attachment To Rebirth"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pi" id="pts-vp-pi3.191"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn23.3:1.1"
msgid "Sāvatthinidānaṃ."
msgstr "At Sāvatthī."

msgctxt "sn23.3:1.2"
msgid "Ekamantaṃ nisinno kho āyasmā rādho bhagavantaṃ etadavoca:"
msgstr "Seated to one side, Venerable Rādha said to the Buddha:"

#. VAR: bhavanettinirodho → bhavanetti (bj, s1-3, km) | bhavanettī (pts1)
#. VAR: bhavanettinirodho’ti → bhavanettīti (bj, s1-3, km) | bhavanettīnirodhoti (pts1)
msgctxt "sn23.3:1.3"
msgid "“‘bhavanettinirodho, bhavanettinirodho’ti, bhante, vuccati."
msgstr ""
"“Sir, they speak of this thing called ‘the cessation of attachment to "
"rebirth’."

msgctxt "sn23.3:1.4"
msgid "Katamā nu kho, bhante, bhavanetti, katamo bhavanettinirodho”ti?"
msgstr ""
"What is the attachment to rebirth? And what is the cessation of attachment "
"to rebirth?”"

msgctxt "sn23.3:1.5"
msgid ""
"“Rūpe kho, rādha, yo chando yo rāgo yā nandī yā taṇhā ye upayupādānā cetaso "
"adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā—"
msgstr ""
"“Rādha, any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for form; and any "
"attraction, grasping, mental dedication, insistence, and underlying "
"tendencies—"

msgctxt "sn23.3:1.6"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati bhavanetti."
msgstr "this is called the attachment to rebirth."

#. VAR: nirodho → nirodhā (bj, s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "sn23.3:1.7"
msgid "Tesaṃ nirodho bhavanettinirodho."
msgstr "Their cessation is the cessation of attachment to rebirth."

msgctxt "sn23.3:1.8"
msgid "Vedanāya …"
msgstr "Any desire, greed, relishing, and craving for feeling …"

msgctxt "sn23.3:1.9"
msgid "saññāya …"
msgstr "perception …"

msgctxt "sn23.3:1.10"
msgid "saṅkhāresu …"
msgstr "choices …"

msgctxt "sn23.3:1.11"
msgid "viññāṇe yo chando … pe … adhiṭṭhānābhinivesānusayā—"
msgstr ""
"consciousness; and any becoming involved, grasping, mental dedication, "
"insistence, and underlying tendencies—"

msgctxt "sn23.3:1.12"
msgid "ayaṃ vuccati bhavanetti."
msgstr "this is called the attachment to rebirth."

msgctxt "sn23.3:1.13"
msgid "Tesaṃ nirodho bhavanettinirodho”ti."
msgstr "Their cessation is the cessation of attachment to rebirth.”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "sn23.3:1.14"
msgid "Tatiyaṃ."
msgstr ""
